title: Talking Critical Role - Battle Royale
description: Brian Wayne Foster is joined by guests Taliesin Jaffe, Matthew Mercer, and Marisha Ray to discuss their time at MomoCon, the epic Critical Role Battle Royale, and give out prizes to fans!
